      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ？\n出版社側に、違う構図を提案したい？",
      "startTime": 2.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "どういうことでしょう\nさっきの私の仕事に、何か不備でもありましたか？",
      "startTime": 8.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳ではないんですが……俺は、出来れば\nアイドルには素の表情を見せてほしいと思ってます",
      "startTime": 16.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきのカメラテストも、とても良かったですけど\n本当のmihoさんとはやっぱり違うなと",
      "startTime": 22.8649967946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスの、素の表情？　……そんなの表に出した途端\n星見プロの信頼も全て失うことになると思いますけど",
      "startTime": 32.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "自分でそれを言いますか……\nま……まぁ、出来る範囲ということで",
      "startTime": 39.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、{user}さんが考える\n私の素顔というのは、どんなろくでもないものですか？",
      "startTime": 46.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……さっきの、ため息をついてた顔\nあっちの方がずっと、mihoさんらしいと思います",
      "startTime": 54.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……喧嘩を売るつもりもなく、そういうことを言う\n度胸だけは大したものだと思いますが",
      "startTime": 61.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "つまり……ウエディングドレスでため息をつくような\n状況を考えて、向こうに提案したいということですか",
      "startTime": 68.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。そういうことです\nもちろんmihoさんが嫌でなければですが……",
      "startTime": 76.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……ウエディングドレスを着る時は\n未来の話をしていると、貴方がさっき言ったんでしょう",
      "startTime": 83.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "ましてや、ブライダル情報誌で\nそんなもの、通る訳がないと思いますが",
      "startTime": 90.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、マリッジブルーがどうこうって\n前にmihoさんが話してたでしょう",
      "startTime": 96.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "結婚するけど、ちょっと不安もある花嫁さんという\n構図なら、mihoさんにも合うんじゃないかと",
      "startTime": 103.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……雑誌の内容やテキスト次第ですけど\nそのくらいなら、なんとかなるかもしれませんね",
      "startTime": 111.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "通るかはともかく、話してみる分には構わないのでは",
      "startTime": 114.6115863164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 118.9887970448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "……辛気くさいと、あの二人には散々言われますけど\nこの顔なりに、使い道というのはあるものですね",
      "startTime": 124.6736772969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それを考えるのが、マネージャーの俺の仕事ですから",
      "startTime": 128.6551916043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（俺の提案は、出版社の担当者をだいぶ困らせたものの）\n（別にページを取って、載せてもらえることになった）",
      "startTime": 140.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "それでは本番、お願いします",
      "startTime": 143.724533836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "結婚はゴールではなくて\n新たな生活の始まりに過ぎませんから",
      "startTime": 150.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "期待と同じくらい、不安だってあると思うんです\n今までの生活との別れの時でもある訳で",
      "startTime": 158.2666575114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "結婚してからのトラブルなんて\n実際、いくらでもあるでしょうしね",
      "startTime": 163.399110455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "ですから期待と……なかなか人には言えない\n式の華やかさとは裏腹の不安を出したいですね",
      "startTime": 170.9666514078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、不安なだけでは、救いがないですし\nそこから立ち上がるところまで、表現出来たらと……",
      "startTime": 178.5333007811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（うん、やっぱり凄くいい表情だ。結婚とは違うけど）\n（……mihoさんも、辛い別れを経験した）",
      "startTime": 188.9333038328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、その悲しみを振り切って再び立ち上がって）\n（新たなグループの一員として、今ここに立ってる）",
      "startTime": 196.3666341143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（だから、その姿が一層映えるのかもしれない）\n（……再起までのやり方は、俺とは相容れないにせよ）",
      "startTime": 205.8666310625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon"
    },
